# Decompose a UCI move into the ordered list of primitive PieceActions the arm
# must execute. Computed on the board state BEFORE the move is pushed, then the
# move is pushed. World xyz for each action is filled from board_coordinates.yaml.

# Move to realise, in UCI, e.g. "e2e4", "e1g1" (castle), "e7e8q" (promotion).
string uci
---
bool ok                               # true if the move decomposed successfully
chess_arm_interfaces/PieceAction[] actions  # ordered manipulation steps
string message                        # human-readable detail / error reason
